706090f-b.title: Brooklyn: Nostrand Avenue - Lincoln Road
706090f-b.text:
(1)
Nostrand Ave., east side, between Lincoln Road and Maple Street,
showing the R.C. Church of St. Francis of -ssisi, as seen from Maple
Street, which is in the foreground.
March 29, 1932.
P. L. Sperr.
(2)
The same, as seen from Lincoln Road.
March 29, 1932.
P. L. Sperr.
